- Install JDK-1.7u51+
- Install git 1.9.0+
- Install IntelliJ Idea community edition 13.0.2+
- From within Idea, install latest Scala plugin
- Clone this repo: git clone https://github.com/mushtaq/scala-basics-1.git
- cd scala-basics-1
- ./sbt gen-idea (will take couple of minutes to complete)
- From within idea, open project and select scala-basics-1 folder
- Install scala 2.10.3 from http://www.scala-lang.org/download/2.10.3.html
